snippet.title: Best VGM 361 - Dragon Quest IV - Wagon Wheel's March
snippet.description:
Symphonic Suite version here: http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=qA6IfcvX_bU

See also:
Best VGM 449 - http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ErlBKXnOHiQ

A collection of my favorite videogame music. Note that most of them are from games I played so I might miss some great ones from games I never played.

NES
Dragon Quest IV
Wagon Wheel's March
